data.description: *Dream Home for the Green Thumb Buyer* Truly enjoy this Spring season with your own Strawberry, Raspberry & Sunflower Patches, PLUS Peach & Apple trees! This lovely SOLAR energized ranch home includes a fully fenced backyard w/ ample gardening space, several XL planters, a productive chicken coop, multi vehicle parking, RV / Boat parking, attached 2 car garage w/ storage & workbenches. Main floor features a convenient front living rm, functional kitchen w/dining room slider to back patio, primary bedroom w/ ensuite bath & walk in closet, plus two bedrooms w/ a shared full bath. Expansive basement features an oversized utility room doubling as workshop, bonus room w/ built-in office space, multiple guest rooms, upgraded full bath with walk-in tile shower, and a cozy comfortable media room
